snippet.title: Resonance of the Ocean - Make musical instruments and answer the echoes heard from beyond the ocean!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://uimss.itch.io/resonance-of-the-ocean?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt A sound reverberated from beyond the ocean.

At the edge of a desolate island, pick up what the waves wash ashore to make instruments. Use those instruments to answer the echoes heard from beyond the ocean.

In this hand-drawn world, enjoy a soothing soundscape formed by waves, footsteps and the sounds made from things washed up.

➡️ More from Image Labo https://uimss.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More adventure games https://itch.io/games/genre-adventure?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
